text: Cool on the hottest days.. Surprised! This place charged at normal rate for entrance fee. There are 2 olympics pools size, 1 children pool, waterplay like slides and massaging pool,low price with amazing facilities,good place for family with children as well.
six out of eight slides are closed for "maintenance". staff is constantly busy with micro managing. Place only suitable for locals, who like their kids to be robots.
